                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 817.51/1015</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to Minister
                            <persName type="to">Jefferson</persName>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1917-10-16T14:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 16, 1917, 2 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your October 12, 9 a.m. What arrangements have been made by Nicaraguan Government
                    for application to awards of Mixed Claims Commission and of Public Credit
                    Commission, of money now held by Ham on account of Ethelburga interests.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Lansing</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
